  "title": "Assistant Engineer (Mechanical)",
  "description": "<p>Roles & Responsibilities</p><p>*Assist in installation, maintenance, and troubleshooting of mechanical systems.</p><p>*Support senior engineers in project execution and site coordination.</p><p>*Conduct inspections, testing, and routine maintenance works.</p><p>*Prepare technical reports, drawings, and documentation.</p><p>*Must have AutoCAD and SolidWorks software knowledge.</p><p>*Able to read and understand mechanical drawing.</p><p>*Have minimum Diploma and above.</p><p>*With hand on experience in machinery.</p><p>*Able to commit in overtime if work require.</p><p>*Other ad hoc duties<br /><br /><br />Lye Chong Herng (R1657957)</p><p>Business Edge Personnel Services Pte Ltd (96C4864)</p>",
